<help general deals>

You can get special deals on certain types of houses and shops.

Houses:

Affordable-class, five rooms, highest-quality door, one no battle room:
450,000

Garland, ten rooms, highest-quality door, twenty pound locked storage box:
2,200,000


Shops:

Affordable-class, level ten shopkeeper, haven, no magic:  1,500,000
 
Affordable-class, level thirty shopkeeper:  500,000

All shop and house deals are upgradeable for the normal prices.

<color=red>
See Also:  houses shops derelicts
</color></help>